Microsoft Entra Domain Services creates a managed domain based on Entra ID identities.

It automatically provides:

* Domain join
* Group Policy
* LDAP
* NTLM/Kerberos

For example, virtual machines can join the managed domain without traditional domain controllers.

# Real-Life Use Case:
A real-life use case is migrating traditional apps to Azure.

# Real-Life Example:
Another example is supporting domain-dependent applications.

This service reduces operational complexity.
